9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"Kokuho | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"Nagasaki, 1964: Following the death of his yakuza father, 15-year-old Kikuo is taken under the wing of a famous kabuki actor. Alongside Shunsuke, the actor’s only son, he decides to dedicate himself to this traditional form of theatre. For decades, the two young men grow and evolve together – and one will become the greatest Japanese master of the art of kabuki."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/110523/kokuho"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"Kokuho"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"Nagasaki, 1964: Following the death of his yakuza father, 15-year-old Kikuo is taken under the wing of a famous kabuki actor. Alongside Shunsuke, the actor’s only son, he decides to dedicate himself to this traditional form of theatre. For decades, the two young men grow and evolve together – and one will become the greatest Japanese master of the art of kabuki."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/110523/kokuho"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/a15F5KJ4mleusJR1YKP4zUyZaxG.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"Kokuho"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"Nagasaki, 1964: Following the death of his yakuza father, 15-year-old Kikuo is taken under the wing of a famous kabuki actor. Alongside Shunsuke, the actor’s only son, he decides to dedicate himself to this traditional form of theatre. For decades, the two young men gr